lish <i>burh</i> ‘stronghold, fortified place’ + <i>dūn</i> ‘hill’; Burdon in Tyne and Wear is named with Old English <i>b̄re</i> ‘byre’ + <i>denu</i> ‘valley’."]}]},{"name":"John","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["New Testament: ‘God is gracious’.  See  <b>John</b> ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs John Bourdon III was born in 1280, in Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with John Bourdon III."},"et":{"1280–":"1280–Surnud","1275–Male":"1275–Surnud","1300–Male":"1300–Surnud","1280–Female":"1280–Surnud","1300":"1300","1275":"1275","1280":"1280","Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England":"Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England"},"fi":{"1280–":"1280–Kuollut","1275–Male":"1275–Kuollut","1300–Male":"1300–Kuollut","1280–Female":"1280–Kuollut","1300":"1300","1275":"1275","1280":"1280","Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England":"Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England"},"fr":{"1280–":"1280–Décédée","1275–Male":"1275–Décédé","1300–Male":"1300–Décédé","1280–Female":"1280–Décédée","1300":"1300","1275":"1275","1280":"1280","Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England":"Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Mrs John Bourdon III est née en 1280, à Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec John Bourdon III."},"de":{"1280–":"1280–Verstorben","1275–Male":"1275–Verstorben","1300–Male":"1300–Verstorben","1280–Female":"1280–Verstorben","1300":"1300","1275":"1275","1280":"1280","Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England":"Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England","lifeSummary":"Mrs John Bourdon III wurde 1280 in Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hatte mit John Bourdon III mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"1280–":"1280–Desede","1275–Male":"1275–Desede","1300–Male":"1300–Desede","1280–Female":"1280–Desede","1300":"1300","1275":"1275","1280":"1280","Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England":"Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England"},"hu":{"1280–"